DialogueNode.dialogue: Good morning Alex, how was meeting everyone?
It was great! Everyone was very friendly.
That's great to hear! I'm glad I brought you on board. We need more people like you around here.
That's fine. I'm sure you'll get it sorted out quickly though. I hired you for a reason, Alex.
Ah, well, it was your first day. It happens to everyone. I'm sure you'll get adjusted quickly enough though. Everyone is pretty friendly here.
Thank you sir, I'll make sure to do my best!
I know you will! Now get back to work, and enjoy the rest of your day.
There's a reason I hired you Alex. There's something I see in you. I know you're the right person for the job!
I think I'm going to enjoy my time here.
Everyone is pretty friendly, but starting a new job is always a different experience.
Everyone seems nice enough but I was a bit nervous.
